channel.description:
Important Notice: If an agency or product owner does not want any publishment, it is withdrawn back. Please send a private youtube message!

Brilliant Ads; Exclusive High-Quality Brillant TV Advertising, Spot And Commercials Channel.

Our goal is to share quality advertises that people have overlooked and therefore contribute to the sector.
At the materials that we use while sharing, detailed information of the advertising companies product or the topic is published. Also the very detailed information about the advertise creators is included. This way communication between different advertisers is ensured.

Also copyright of companies is held forefront.
The product that is being advertised and the company info is at the beginning of the videos name. Video details are filled with product and creators' information.
channel.title: Brilliant Ads
